<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Amberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Auszahlung eines verbrieften Leibgedinges für Margarethe Topler, Witwe des Hans Topler, Bürgerin zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_418" id="208v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_418_r1l17">Der Stat cʒu <expan>Amb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_418_r1l18"><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> vns hat fürgelegt fraw Margret des <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l19">Toplers <expan>ſelıge<ex>n</ex></expan> witib <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin / vvie daʒ ſıe leipgeding </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l20">von ew / hab / 
<del rend="strikethrough">daſſelb Jr leipgeding Jr </del> als ſıe des gut brıef </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l22">vnd vrkunde hab / das Jr ir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒiehet</expan> vnd Jr des niht <expan>becʒale<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l23">wöllet / Als <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_418_line_1576425586306_4996">Jr </ab></add> brief auſʒvveyſen / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr der <expan>egen<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l24"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgerin / daſſelb Jr <expan>leipg<ex>eding</ex></expan> <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogenlıch</expan> richten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l25">vnd becʒalen wöllet / nach <expan>ır<ex>er</ex></expan> brief laut vnd ſag / Alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_418_r1l26">daʒ ſıe vnklaghaft darümb werde / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_418" id="208v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu <expan>Amb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt fraw Margret, des
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Toplers
                            <expan>selige<ex>n</ex></expan> witib, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        burgerin, wie daz sie leipgeding von ew hab, als sie des gut brief und
                        urkunde hab, das ir ir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cziehet</expan> und ir des niht
                                <expan>beczale<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, als
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>ir</add> brief auszweysen. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir der
                                <expan>egen<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgerin dasselb ir
                                <expan>leipg<ex>eding</ex></expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogenlich</expan> richten und beczalen wöllet nach
                                <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> brief laut und sag, also daz sie
                        unklaghaft darümb werde. Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
